Jodi: Yeah, I would be happy to. So 'The Storyteller' is really the story of Sage Singer. She's a 23-year old baker in a small New England town and she's a bit of a recluse; she has a scar on her face, she doesn't get along with people and she's attending a grief group because her mother recently passed away.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:52.000
Jodi: There she meets an unlikely friend, 95-year-old Josef Weber, who is everyone's favourite adoptive grandpa, retired teacher ... a good guy in the town.

00:00:55.417 --> 00:01:02.417
