00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:31.560
BBC Host: It's quite horrific, some of the details, isn't it? Did you speak with lots of survivors?

00:01:40.583 --> 00:01:47.583
Jodi: I did. I did research with multiple Holocaust survivors, and of course, hearing them tell their stories and crying with them, and reliving them, was extremely emotional and difficult. There was a man named Bernie whose father was shot to death in front of him.

00:01:47.583 --> 00:01:52.514
